title: Ep. 439 - ISIS Is Dead, Kanye Is Alive
description:
President Trump has announced that the leader of ISIS was killed. We examine the gory details, and what it means for US foreign policy, and what it means for the media coverage of US foreign policy. Then, Congressman Katie Hill resigns from Congress after details of her creepy and exploitative relationship with a staffer come out. We analyze the double standards of the sexual revolution. Finally, Kanye West comes home to Jesus! Date: 10-28-2019
